<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 00:30:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡应该为 10 月 7 日的失败负责吗？这些利库德集团选民宁愿相信阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bibis-to-blame-for-oct-7-failures-likud-voters-prefer-to-believe-conspiracy-theories/0000018b-90c2-d477-a1ff-f7c2b8d10000</link><description>利库德集团在民调中的支持率大幅下滑，广大公众对政府感到愤怒。但对该党的一些传统据点的（有点危险的）访问揭示了为什么有些人仍然支持内塔尼亚胡——即使是现在</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 23:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bibis-to-blame-for-oct-7-failures-likud-voters-prefer-to-believe-conspiracy-theories/0000018b-90c2-d477-a1ff-f7c2b8d10000</guid></item><item><title>大卫·彼得雷乌斯将军向以色列发出警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/gen-david-petraeus-has-a-warning-for-israel/0000018b-96c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb0e090000</link><description>在这些战争期间指挥美国陆军的戴维·彼得雷乌斯将军表示，当以色列陷入加沙“异常艰难”的战场时，以色列军队必须从美国打击基地组织和伊斯兰国的痛苦经历中吸取教训</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 20:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/gen-david-petraeus-has-a-warning-for-israel/0000018b-96c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb0e090000</guid></item><item><title>作为大屠杀幸存者，我对以色列联合国特使的耻辱感到悲痛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-a-holocaust-survivor-im-saddened-by-the-israeli-un-envoys-disgrace/0000018b-9655-db71-a7df-ffdde0c20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 20:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-a-holocaust-survivor-im-saddened-by-the-israeli-un-envoys-disgrace/0000018b-9655-db71-a7df-ffdde0c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列驱逐了自战争开始以来滞留在约旦河西岸的数千名加沙工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-deports-thousands-of-gazan-workers-stuck-in-west-bank-since-start-of-war/0000018b-95fd-db7e-af9b-ffff3d2f0000</link><description>战争爆发时，国家取消了滞留在以色列的劳工的工作许可证。在安全内阁决定驱逐他们并阻止加沙工人未来进入以色列后，将这些工人送回加沙成为可能</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 16:48:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-deports-thousands-of-gazan-workers-stuck-in-west-bank-since-start-of-war/0000018b-95fd-db7e-af9b-ffff3d2f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加沙战争需要暂停以防止宗教战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-gaza-war-needs-a-humanitarian-pause-to-prevent-a-religious-war/0000018b-9596-db7e-af9b-ffd767a90000</link><description>埃及和沙特阿拉伯告诉华盛顿，加沙危机可能会复活极端组织，而人道主义暂停可能会维护对哈马斯战争的合法性</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 16:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-gaza-war-needs-a-humanitarian-pause-to-prevent-a-religious-war/0000018b-9596-db7e-af9b-ffd767a90000</guid></item><item><title>在反犹太主义抬头之际，以色列呼吁海外公民淡化“犹太人或以色列身份”的公开标志</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-03/ty-article/as-antisemitism-rises-israel-tells-citizens-abroad-to-downplay-jewish-or-israeli-identity/0000018b-95c4-d8a6-a38b-dfd7bc6c0000</link><description>以色列外交部建议公民推迟前往有旅行警告的国家；要求避免外化以色列和犹太符号，找出紧急服务的电话号码，并远离示威活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-03/ty-article/as-antisemitism-rises-israel-tells-citizens-abroad-to-downplay-jewish-or-israeli-identity/0000018b-95c4-d8a6-a38b-dfd7bc6c0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党纳斯鲁拉赞扬哈马斯 10 月 7 日的“英勇”袭击，称这是“100% 巴勒斯坦人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/hezbollahs-nasrallah-praises-heroic-oct-7-hamas-attack-says-it-was-100-palestinian/0000018b-95a4-db71-a7df-fded25b30000</link><description>真主党领导人赞扬哈马斯的袭击如何导致以色列发生“地震”，并警告说“那些想要防止地区战争的人必须迅速停止对加沙的侵略”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/hezbollahs-nasrallah-praises-heroic-oct-7-hamas-attack-says-it-was-100-palestinian/0000018b-95a4-db71-a7df-fded25b30000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在以色列访问期间敦促内塔尼亚胡在加沙“暂停人道主义行动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-pushes-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-during-israel-visit/0000018b-959f-db7e-af9b-ffdfa23a0000</link><description>这是美国国务卿自战争开始以来第三次访问以色列，他在会见内塔尼亚胡后表示，需要采取更多行动来“保护巴勒斯坦平民”。布林肯还指出，“屠杀的残酷性在许多人的记忆中很快就消失了”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-pushes-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-during-israel-visit/0000018b-959f-db7e-af9b-ffdfa23a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙援助组织正在努力估计破坏程度。他们说情况从未如此糟糕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-aid-groups-struggle-to-estimate-extent-of-destruction-they-say-its-never-been-worse/0000018b-953e-d7a8-afcf-bfbf5b350000</link><description>在前几轮战争中，加沙地带的组织设法记录了损失，但现在他们甚至很难与员工保持联系。当以色列质疑加沙地带报告的伤亡人数时，组织表示数据可靠</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-aid-groups-struggle-to-estimate-extent-of-destruction-they-say-its-never-been-worse/0000018b-953e-d7a8-afcf-bfbf5b350000</guid></item><item><title>“我再也不会好起来了：”以色列的新移民如何应对战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-never-going-to-be-okay-again-how-new-immigrants-to-israel-are-coping-with-the-war/0000018b-8fa0-d477-a1ff-ffa057ef0000</link><description>《国土报》采访了近年来移居以色列的六名移民，以了解他们在战时的新家园最让他们惊讶的是什么。尽管如此，没有人后悔选择搬到这里</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 14:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-never-going-to-be-okay-again-how-new-immigrants-to-israel-are-coping-with-the-war/0000018b-8fa0-d477-a1ff-ffa057ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可能为参与10月7日大屠杀的哈马斯恐怖分子设立特别法庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-may-establish-special-court-for-hamas-terrorists-who-took-part-in-massacres/0000018b-94c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb00bd0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列在加沙边境附近的社区关押了数百名涉嫌参与哈马斯屠杀的人，并一直在系统地收集战争罪和反人类罪的数字证据</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 12:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-may-establish-special-court-for-hamas-terrorists-who-took-part-in-massacres/0000018b-94c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb00bd0000</guid></item><item><title>看到南部的恐怖，以色列北部的居民感到他们必须自力更生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/seeing-the-horrors-in-the-south-galilee-residents-feel-they-must-fend-for-themselves/0000018b-9469-db7e-af9b-ffebd7ad0000</link><description>私人拖拉机挖的战壕、临时搭建的射击阵地以及自愿担任观察员的平民：西加利利和上加利利的居民不再相信国家会保护他们。一位居民说，“感觉我们又回到了建州前的日子”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 11:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/seeing-the-horrors-in-the-south-galilee-residents-feel-they-must-fend-for-themselves/0000018b-9469-db7e-af9b-ffebd7ad0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部：约旦河西岸与以色列军队的冲突造成六人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-six-killed-in-west-bank-clashes-with-israeli-army/0000018b-94af-db71-a7df-fdefff020000</link><description>位于拉马拉的巴勒斯坦权力机构卫生部表示，所有六人均死于与以色列国防军冲突中的枪伤，其中两人在杰宁，两人在希伯伦附近</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 10:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-six-killed-in-west-bank-clashes-with-israeli-army/0000018b-94af-db71-a7df-fdefff020000</guid></item><item><title>又有五名以色列士兵在加沙地面行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/five-additional-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-948a-db7e-af9b-ffcbbc660000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了5名阵亡士兵的姓名，使加沙地面行动开始以来阵亡士兵总数达到24人</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 10:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/five-additional-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-948a-db7e-af9b-ffcbbc660000</guid></item><item><title>美国正在缓慢而谨慎地在加沙问题上为以色列划定红线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-slowly-and-carefully-drawing-red-lines-for-israel-on-gaza/0000018b-9414-db71-a7df-fdddf39d0000</link><description>最近一周，白宫关于以色列-加沙战争的信息发生了转变，官员们谈到了加沙的人道主义暂停，总统乔·拜登向以色列施压，要求其控制极端主义的约旦河西岸定居者</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 08:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-slowly-and-carefully-drawing-red-lines-for-israel-on-gaza/0000018b-9414-db71-a7df-fdddf39d0000</guid></item><item><title>火箭弹袭击以色列中部特拉维夫；以色列国防军称击中了哈马斯在加沙使用的救护车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-live/blinken-to-push-for-humanitarian-pause-as-israeli-army-encircles-gaza-city/0000018b-9334-db7e-af9b-fbf78ad50000</link><description>真主党纳斯鲁拉在讲话中赞扬哈马斯 10 月 7 日的“英勇”袭击，称这是“100% 巴勒斯坦人”。 ■ 24 名以色列士兵和军官在加沙地面进攻中丧生 ■ 布林肯表示，以色列“需要采取更多措施来保护巴勒斯坦平民” ” 而内塔尼亚胡表示，在人质返回之前不会停火。 ■ 以色列呼吁海外公民淡化其“犹太人或以色列身份”的公开迹象。 ■ 加沙被扣押的 242 名人质，40 人仍然失踪。 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称加沙有超过 9,000 人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-live/blinken-to-push-for-humanitarian-pause-as-israeli-army-encircles-gaza-city/0000018b-9334-db7e-af9b-fbf78ad50000</guid></item><item><title>在东西方之间，内塔尼亚胡现在确实处于自己的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/between-east-and-west-netanyahu-really-now-is-a-league-of-his-own/0000018b-91bc-d477-a1ff-f7bc76240000</link><description>一边是乌克兰和美国，一边是卡塔尔和俄罗斯：一切都在这两个轴心之间进行。 ■ 摩萨德前任主席约西·科恩回归背后的原因是什么？ ■ 斯莫特里奇努力点燃约旦河西岸，同时永远不会忘记照顾他的基地</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/between-east-and-west-netanyahu-really-now-is-a-league-of-his-own/0000018b-91bc-d477-a1ff-f7bc76240000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉期待已久的讲话可能决定战争的进程和黎巴嫩的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-long-awaited-speech-could-dictate-the-course-of-the-war-and-lebanons-future/0000018b-9185-db71-a7df-fdcd1cda0000</link><description>美国在该地区的强大存在使得真主党和伊朗更有可能保持谨慎 ■ 以色列领导人铲除哈马斯的承诺只是口头声明，他们尚未说明如何将其转化为行动 ■ 美国的合作预示着今天的美好前景以色列与哈马斯战争之后</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-long-awaited-speech-could-dictate-the-course-of-the-war-and-lebanons-future/0000018b-9185-db71-a7df-fdcd1cda0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:31:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列为民主而战。现在他正在让它为自己的生命而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</link><description>总理的助手们已经在为内塔尼亚胡战后的政治生存收集弹药，但公众不太可能让他保住自己的席位。他的继任者将不得不面对内塔尼亚胡留下的灾难性遗产</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</guid></item></channel></rss>